    "rationale": "Package accepted under Minimal profile for adversarial sample purposes. All 13 credibility factors have been catalogued with required and achieved levels. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain not-assessed as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The Minimal profile does not mandate a Context of Use object; therefore no hasContextOfUse is present, and the intended-use scope is undefined. This constitutes the W-ON-01 weakener condition.",
